1)(10pts.) Is the propositional formula (A^~B)U(A^C) equivalent to the formula A^(~BUC)?  Write a truth table for both formulas. 

Solution:
A | B | C | (A^~B)U(A^C) | A^(~BUC)
T | T | T |       T      |    T
T | T | F |       F      |    F
T | F | T |       T      |    T
T | F | F |       T      |    T
F | T | T |       F      |    F
F | T | F |       F      |    F
F | F | T |       F      |    F
F | F | F |       F      |    F

Yes, they are equivalent.
